high_descs: Turn left, hang a right at the sink, cross the room to the wall and face the counter to the right.
Pick up the candle holder with a candle behind the gray bottle on the counter top.
Turn around, hang a left at the green door, cross the room and face left at the toilet towards the green cabinets.
Place the candle holder with a candle in the bottom green drawer at the very back left corner and close the drawer.
Turn around and head to the toilet.
Pick up the candle holder with the candle in between two objects on the toilet tank.
Turn around to face the green cabinets.
Place the candle holder with a candle inside the green drawer to the right of the other candle holder at the far back left.
anns.task_desc: Place two candle holders with candles inside a drawer.

high_descs: Turn left and take a step forward, then turn right and walk across the room, turn right to face the dresser.
Pick up the candle that is on the left side of the dresser.
Turn around and start walking forward, the turn left and walk over to the tub, turn left to face the right end of the dresser.
Open the bottom right drawer of the dresser and place the candle inside in the back left corner.
Turn around and walk over to the toilet.
Pick up the candle that is on the toilet tank.
Turn around and walk back over to the right end of the dresser.
Open the bottom right drawer of the dresser and place the candle inside to the right of the candle that is already in there.
anns.task_desc: Move two candles into a drawer.

high_descs: Cross the room, turn to the counter to the right.
Pick up the candlestick in the back of the soap dispenser.
Go to the other end of the counter.
Put the candlestick in the bottom end drawer.
Turn around, walk to the toilet.
Pick up the candlestick next to the soap dispenser.
Turn around, walk back to the counter.
Put the candlestick next to the first candlestick in the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put the two candlesticks in the drawer.
